            <title>[LU-17013] FIEMAP_EXTENT_LAST is missed in some case</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17013</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Call &lt;tt&gt;ioctl(fd, FS_IOC_FIEMAP, fiemap)&lt;/tt&gt; to get the extents of a file. Given the file has &lt;b&gt;N&lt;/b&gt; extents and &lt;tt&gt;fiemap-&amp;gt;fm_extent_count&lt;/tt&gt; is filled with exactly &lt;b&gt;N&lt;/b&gt;, the last extent will not have &lt;tt&gt;FIEMAP_EXTENT_LAST&lt;/tt&gt; flag.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
